Delphine Seyrig https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Delphine_Seyrig 0 Delphine Claire Beltiane Seyrig (French: [sɛʁiɡ]; 10 April 1932 – 15 October 1990) was a Lebanese-born French stage and film actress, a film director and a feminist.
